column5: Any ideas what a 2003 Lund V Rebel SS 1650 with a 25 hp Mercury bigfoot on a trailer is worth. From pictures looks to be in good shape.
I would assume a pretty penny.  Found this 1996 on Ebay for $5,100

Does it come with any accessories? do you know if it leaks? is the lowerend water tight? how many hours? original owner? Console or Tiller? there are alot of variables here...  But I would safely say between 5-10k again depending on the above  MTP just bought a new hull... might give you a better idea..  G
Thanks guys. Gerritt not sure about all the info yet, just looking at possibly importing and making a couple bucks.
lund had a special on for a 16foot with a 50 2stroke plus trailer for around $12,500, you can check their webpage to verify this.
